{"tid":2371881,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉湖山莊3房套單位 放盤3日 [搶盤追價] 653萬元成交","createTime":"2021-01-19T08:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T08:35:00.000Z","uid":73269,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"77a51a9894916f7e0f96659015de20c3e16f3178","tid":2371881,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T08:06:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"> 搶盤追價<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中原地產天水圍柏慧豪園分行副分區營業經理曾芷妍表示，市況升溫，加上農曆新年將至，買家紛紛加快入市步伐。分行新近促成嘉湖山莊麗湖居4座中層A室成交，實用面積638平方呎，三房套房間隔，上周五才放盤，叫價650萬元，周末期間不斷有睇樓客參觀單位，其中一組客人周日睇樓後立即洽購，得知有另一組買家剛表示<span class=\"red\">願意不議價</span>以650萬元承接，便立即追價搶盤，最終成功以653萬元購入單位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.centanet.com/info/property-news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%A8%BF/%E5%98%89%E6%B9%96%E5%B1%B1%E8%8E%8A3%E6%88%BF%E5%A5%97%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D-%E6%94%BE%E7%9B%A43%E6%97%A5-%E6%90%B6%E9%AB%98%E8%87%B3652-8%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4/102152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.centanet.com%2Finfo%2Fproperty-news%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E7%25A8%25BF%2F%25E5%2598%2589%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%258E%258A3%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25A5%2597%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%259B%25A43%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E6%2590%25B6%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2587%25B3652-8%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%2F102152&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=5776826d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.centanet.com/info/property-news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%A8%BF/%E5%98%89%E6%B9%96%E5%B1%B1%E8%8E%8A3%E6%88%BF%E5%A5%97%E